premise_source_doc_sentence: Neal Joseph Schon  (  born February 27 , 1954  )  is an American rock guitarist , songwriter , and vocalist , best known for his work with the bands Journey and Bad English .
He is Journey 's last original constant member , having participated in every album and tour to date .
He was a member of the rock band Santana before forming Journey , and was also an original member of Hardline .
Schon was inducted into the Oklahoma Music Hall of Fame on August 23 , 2013 .
Schon was inducted into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame as a member of Journey on April 7 , 2017 .

Late Nite is the first solo album by Neal Schon released in 1989 .
`` Only the Young '' is a song written by Jonathan Cain , Steve Perry and Neal Schon of the band Journey .
